The capital is Oshakati. Omahangu (pearl millet) is the main staple crop grown in Oshana. Cattle also do well here and there are many herds. There are eleven constituencies: * Okaku * Okatana * Okatyali * Ompundja * Ondangwa Rural * Ondangwa Urban * Ongwediva * Oshakati East * Oshakati West * Uukwiyu * Uuvudhiya ==References==
